{"pageid":15313,"pagename":"Sorcerer's Tower","title":"Sorcerer's Tower","displaytitle":"Sorcerer's Tower","revid":14272989,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"kartographer_frames","value":1},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"Sorcerer's_Tower.png"},{"name":"description","value":"The Sorcerer's Tower is a four-story tower south of Seers' Village. It is the residence of Thormac the sorcerer."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"noexcerpt noprint nomobile rs-external-header-links\" style=\"display:none\"><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rs\" data-text=\"RuneScape\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on Sorcerer&#39;s Tower.\" data-site=\"rs\">The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/Sorcerer%27s_Tower\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:Sorcerer&#39;s Tower\">rsw:Sorcerer's Tower</a></span><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rsc\" data-text=\"CS\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Classic Wiki also has an article on Sorcerors&#39; Tower.\" data-site=\"rsc\">The RuneScape Classic Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://classic.runescape.wiki/w/Sorcerors%27_Tower\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"classicrsw:Sorcerors&#39; Tower\">classicrsw:Sorcerors' Tower</a></span></div>\n<small><div class=\"hatnote\"><i>The wiki defaults to the British convention for <a href=\"/w/RuneScape:Style_guide#Numbers\" title=\"RuneScape:Style guide\">floor numbering</a>: Ground floor, first floor, etc.<span class=\"nomobile\"> This may be changed by clicking the moon icon at the top right of the site.</span></i></div></small>\n<table class=\"rsw-infobox infobox no-parenthesis-style\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-header\">Sorcerer's Tower</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-image infobox-full-width-content\"><a href=\"/w/File:Sorcerer%27s_Tower.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Sorcerer&#39;s Tower.png\" src=\"/images/Sorcerer%27s_Tower.png?f8e8c\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1280\" height=\"950\" data-file-width=\"1280\" data-file-height=\"950\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Released</th><td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/25_March\" title=\"25 March\">25 March</a> <a href=\"/w/2002\" title=\"2002\">2002</a> (<a href=\"/w/Update:Latest_RuneScape_News_(25_March_2002)\" title=\"Update:Latest RuneScape News (25 March 2002)\">Update</a>)</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Members\" title=\"Members\">Members</a></th><td colspan=\"3\">Yes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Location</th><td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Kandarin\" title=\"Kandarin\">Kandarin</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Teleports</th><td colspan=\"3\"><span class=\"fairycode\"><b>B</b><b>L</b><b>R</b></span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Map</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-full-width-content infobox-image\"><a class=\"mw-kartographer-map mw-kartographer-container center\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 250px;background-image: url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_41_53.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_42_53.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_41_52.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-03-23_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_42_52.png); background-position: -162px -79px, 94px -79px, -162px 177px, 94px 177px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\" data-mw=\"interface\" data-style=\"0\" data-width=\"300\" data-height=\"250\" data-zoom=\"2\" data-lat=\"3405\" data-lon=\"2702\" data-mapid=\"0\" data-plane=\"0\" href=\"/w/Special:Map/0/2/-1/2702/3405\"></a></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Advanced data</th></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"2\">Type</th><td colspan=\"3\">building</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<table class=\"relative-location\" style=\"float:right; width:200px; clear:right;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" class=\"relative-location-header\"><span class=\"relative-location-txt\">Location on <b><a href=\"/w/World_Map\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"World Map\"><span class=\"relative-location-txt\">World Map</span></a></b></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/w/Ranging_Guild\" title=\"Ranging Guild\">Ranging Guild</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\">&#8593;\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:25%\"><a href=\"/w/Hemenster\" title=\"Hemenster\">Hemenster</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:7.5%\">&#8592;\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25%; align-items: center;\"><b>Sorcerer's Tower</b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:7.5%\">&#8594;\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25%\"><a href=\"/w/Keep_Le_Faye\" title=\"Keep Le Faye\">Keep Le Faye</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\">&#8595;\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild\" title=\"Legends&#39; Guild\">Legends' Guild</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Sorcerer's Tower</b> is a four-story tower south of <a href=\"/w/Seers%27_Village\" title=\"Seers&#39; Village\">Seers' Village</a>. It is the residence of <a href=\"/w/Thormac\" title=\"Thormac\">Thormac</a> the sorcerer.\n</p><p>The quickest ways to get there are using the <a href=\"/w/Kandarin_headgear\" title=\"Kandarin headgear\">Kandarin headgear</a> 3+ teleport to <a href=\"/w/Sherlock\" title=\"Sherlock\">Sherlock</a>, the <a href=\"/w/Quest_point_cape\" title=\"Quest point cape\">quest point cape</a> teleport to the <a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild\" title=\"Legends&#39; Guild\">Legends' Guild</a>, the fairy ring code <span class=\"fairycode\"><b>B</b><b>L</b><b>R</b></span> to the Legends' Guild; or the <a href=\"/w/Combat_bracelet\" title=\"Combat bracelet\">combat bracelet</a> teleport to the <a href=\"/w/Ranging_Guild\" title=\"Ranging Guild\">Ranging Guild</a>. An alternative way of getting there is to enter the west portal on the <span class=\"floornumber\"><span class=\"floornumber-gb\">2<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">nd</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"British convention; floor 3 in the US\">UK</span>&#93;</sup></span><span class=\"floornumber-us noexcerpt\">3<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">rd</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"US convention; floor 2 in the UK\">US</span>&#93;</sup></span></span> of the <a href=\"/w/Wizards%27_Guild\" title=\"Wizards&#39; Guild\">Wizards' Guild</a>.\n</p><p>At the Sorcerer's Tower, players may begin the <a href=\"/w/Scorpion_Catcher\" title=\"Scorpion Catcher\">Scorpion Catcher</a> quest by talking to Thormac, the completion of which allows the player to pay Thormac 40,000 coins to enchant any <a href=\"/w/Battlestaves\" title=\"Battlestaves\">elemental battlestaff</a> into a <a href=\"/w/Mystic_staff\" title=\"Mystic staff\">mystic staff</a>.\n</p><p>The Sorcerer's Tower used to be popular with players with high <a href=\"/w/Woodcutting\" title=\"Woodcutting\">Woodcutting</a>, as it contains the second largest number of <a href=\"/w/Magic_tree\" title=\"Magic tree\">magic trees</a> in one area (4), as well as being fairly easily accessible. There are also three magic trees directly north-east, behind the tower. Since the addition of the <a href=\"/w/Woodcutting_guild\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Woodcutting guild\">Woodcutting guild</a>, it has become deserted.\n</p><p>There is also a <a href=\"/w/Knife\" title=\"Knife\">knife</a> spawn at the <span class=\"floornumber\"><span class=\"floornumber-gb\">ground&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"British convention; floor 1 in the US\">UK</span>&#93;</sup></span><span class=\"floornumber-us noexcerpt\">1<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">st</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"US convention; ground floor in the UK\">US</span>&#93;</sup></span></span> and 3 <a href=\"/w/Flax\" title=\"Flax\">flax</a> plants in the garden where the Magic Trees are. The closest bank to the Sorcerer's Tower is inside the <a href=\"/w/Legends%27_Guild\" title=\"Legends&#39; Guild\">Legends' Guild</a>. The second closest bank is in <a href=\"/w/Seers%27_Village\" title=\"Seers&#39; Village\">Seers' Village</a>.\n</p><p>A clue from a <a href=\"/w/Clue_scroll\" title=\"Clue scroll\">clue scroll</a> leads to the <span class=\"floornumber\"><span class=\"floornumber-gb\">1<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">st</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"British convention; floor 2 in the US\">UK</span>&#93;</sup></span><span class=\"floornumber-us noexcerpt\">2<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">nd</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"US convention; floor 1 in the UK\">US</span>&#93;</sup></span></span> of this tower. \"Read 'how to breed scorpions' by O.W.Thathurt\", Search the northern bookcase on the <span class=\"floornumber\"><span class=\"floornumber-gb\">1<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">st</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"British convention; floor 2 in the US\">UK</span>&#93;</sup></span><span class=\"floornumber-us noexcerpt\">2<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">nd</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"US convention; floor 1 in the UK\">US</span>&#93;</sup></span></span> to unlock the next <a href=\"/w/Clue_scroll\" title=\"Clue scroll\">clue scroll</a> in your <a href=\"/w/Treasure_trail\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Treasure trail\">treasure trail</a>.\n</p><p>The music track <a href=\"/w/Magical_Journey\" title=\"Magical Journey\">Magical Journey</a> is unlocked when first entering the tower.\n</p>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Scorpion Catcher\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Scorpion_Catcher\" title=\"Template:Scorpion Catcher\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Scorpion_Catcher\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Scorpion_Catcher?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a href=\"/w/Scorpion_Catcher\" title=\"Scorpion Catcher\">Scorpion Catcher</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">NPCs</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Thormac\" title=\"Thormac\"><img alt=\"Thormac chathead.png: Chat head image of Thormac\" src=\"/images/thumb/Thormac_chathead.png/21px-Thormac_chathead.png?51253\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Thormac_chathead.png/32px-Thormac_chathead.png?51253 1.5x, /images/thumb/Thormac_chathead.png/42px-Thormac_chathead.png?51253 2x\" data-file-width=\"119\" data-file-height=\"198\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Thormac\" title=\"Thormac\">Thormac</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Velrak_the_explorer\" title=\"Velrak the explorer\"><img alt=\"Velrak the explorer chathead.png: Chat head image of Velrak the explorer\" src=\"/images/thumb/Velrak_the_explorer_chathead.png/23px-Velrak_the_explorer_chathead.png?1180d\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"23\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Velrak_the_explorer_chathead.png/35px-Velrak_the_explorer_chathead.png?1180d 1.5x, /images/thumb/Velrak_the_explorer_chathead.png/46px-Velrak_the_explorer_chathead.png?1180d 2x\" data-file-width=\"85\" data-file-height=\"129\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Velrak_the_explorer\" title=\"Velrak the explorer\">Velrak the explorer</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Peksa\" title=\"Peksa\"><img alt=\"Peksa chathead.png: Chat head image of Peksa\" src=\"/images/thumb/Peksa_chathead.png/33px-Peksa_chathead.png?8d36b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"33\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Peksa_chathead.png/50px-Peksa_chathead.png?8d36b 1.5x, /images/thumb/Peksa_chathead.png/66px-Peksa_chathead.png?8d36b 2x\" data-file-width=\"131\" data-file-height=\"139\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Peksa\" title=\"Peksa\">Peksa</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Abbot_Langley\" title=\"Abbot Langley\"><img alt=\"Abbot Langley chathead.png: Chat head image of Abbot Langley\" src=\"/images/thumb/Abbot_Langley_chathead.png/27px-Abbot_Langley_chathead.png?47c15\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"27\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Abbot_Langley_chathead.png/40px-Abbot_Langley_chathead.png?47c15 1.5x, /images/thumb/Abbot_Langley_chathead.png/53px-Abbot_Langley_chathead.png?47c15 2x\" data-file-width=\"62\" data-file-height=\"81\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Abbot_Langley\" title=\"Abbot Langley\">Abbot Langley</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Barbarian_guard\" title=\"Barbarian guard\"><img alt=\"Barbarian guard chathead.png: Chat head image of Barbarian guard\" src=\"/images/thumb/Barbarian_guard_chathead.png/41px-Barbarian_guard_chathead.png?3ff4a\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"41\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Barbarian_guard_chathead.png/63px-Barbarian_guard_chathead.png?3ff4a 1.5x, /images/thumb/Barbarian_guard_chathead.png/83px-Barbarian_guard_chathead.png?3ff4a 2x\" data-file-width=\"144\" data-file-height=\"122\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Barbarian_guard\" title=\"Barbarian guard\">Barbarian guard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Seer\" title=\"Seer\">Seer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Jailer\" title=\"Jailer\">Jailer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Kharid_Scorpion\" title=\"Kharid Scorpion\">Kharid Scorpion</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Items</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Scorpion_cage\" title=\"Scorpion cage\"><img alt=\"Scorpion cage (empty).png\" src=\"/images/Scorpion_cage_%28empty%29.png?3f71e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"28\" height=\"24\" data-file-width=\"28\" data-file-height=\"24\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Scorpion_cage\" title=\"Scorpion cage\">Scorpion cage</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Related</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Scorpion_Catcher/Quick_guide\" title=\"Scorpion Catcher/Quick guide\">Quick Guide</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐67df7655d‐czd4b\nCached time: 20220420203404\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.101 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.138 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 335/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 17740/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 612/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 778/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.028/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1670114/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   76.668      1 -total\n 34.05%   26.105      1 Template:Infobox_Location\n 21.54%   16.518      1 Template:Scorpion_Catcher\n 19.27%   14.775      1 Template:External\n 15.29%   11.726      4 Template:FloorNumber\n 13.86%   10.630      1 Template:Navbox\n 10.29%    7.893      1 Template:Map\n  5.72%    4.387      1 Template:Relativelocation\n  5.67%    4.348      1 Template:Ctg\n  5.30%    4.065      2 Template:Fairycode\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:15313-0!canonical and timestamp 20220420203404 and revision id 14272989. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{External|rs|rsc=Sorcerors' Tower}}\n{{floor}}\n{{Infobox Location\n|name = Sorcerer's Tower\n|image = [[File:Sorcerer's Tower.png]]\n|release = [[25 March]] [[2002]]\n|update = Latest RuneScape News (25 March 2002)\n|members = Yes\n|location = [[Kandarin]]\n|teleport = {{Fairycode|BLR}}\n|map = {{Map|name=Sorcerer's Tower|x=2702|y=3405|height=250|zoom=2}}\n|type = building\n}}\n{{Relativelocation\n|location = Sorcerer's Tower\n|north = Ranging Guild\n|west = Hemenster\n|south = Legends' Guild\n|east = Keep Le Faye\n}}\nThe '''Sorcerer's Tower''' is a four-story tower south of [[Seers' Village]]. It is the residence of [[Thormac]] the sorcerer.\n\nThe quickest ways to get there are using the [[Kandarin headgear]] 3+ teleport to [[Sherlock]], the [[quest point cape]] teleport to the [[Legends' Guild]], the fairy ring code {{Fairycode|BLR}} to the Legends' Guild; or the [[combat bracelet]] teleport to the [[Ranging Guild]]. An alternative way of getting there is to enter the west portal on the {{FloorNumber|uk=2}} of the [[Wizards' Guild]].\n\nAt the Sorcerer's Tower, players may begin the [[Scorpion Catcher]] quest by talking to Thormac, the completion of which allows the player to pay Thormac 40,000 coins to enchant any [[battlestaves|elemental battlestaff]] into a [[mystic staff]].\n\nThe Sorcerer's Tower used to be popular with players with high [[Woodcutting]], as it contains the second largest number of [[magic tree]]s in one area (4), as well as being fairly easily accessible. There are also three magic trees directly north-east, behind the tower. Since the addition of the [[Woodcutting guild]], it has become deserted.\n\nThere is also a [[knife]] spawn at the {{FloorNumber|uk=0}} and 3 [[flax]] plants in the garden where the Magic Trees are. The closest bank to the Sorcerer's Tower is inside the [[Legends' Guild]]. The second closest bank is in [[Seers' Village]].\n\nA clue from a [[clue scroll]] leads to the {{FloorNumber|uk=1}} of this tower. \"Read 'how to breed scorpions' by O.W.Thathurt\", Search the northern bookcase on the {{FloorNumber|uk=1}} to unlock the next [[clue scroll]] in your [[treasure trail]].\n\nThe music track [[Magical Journey]] is unlocked when first entering the tower.\n\n{{Scorpion Catcher}}\n[[Category:Kandarin]]"}